 />\n又要另外再搵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n都完全唔係個回事。<br />\n關心一線嘅人唔會同你建立關係，<br />\nsupport group 應該係好似教會咁，<br />\n大家都係弟兄姊妹，可以互相依靠，<br />\n但重點係唔好硬性要人信果個教。<br />\n<br />\n香港社會太少呢d 野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔好要人搵代替品先，<br />\n我覺得係時候有人initiate.<br />\n<br />\n利申願意做其中一個"},{"pid":"f9e2938ad754be11792baf586c26904aaa3f814e","tid":2180041,"uid":274732,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7435d03dc916e14e3a81b05c2190ecf1883bbe2b","tid":2180041,"uid":217128,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"a5ff4cdf095450f1aafba2d5e910ecd1cae5b427","tid":2180041,"uid":274732,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"3309fc5f0c0ee80b2b273b5927df85074df3006b","tid":2180041,"uid":217128,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-29T19:31:14.000Z","msg":"做到。我覺得搞嘅人要有多d 知識，<br />\n知識層面上由心理學、哲學、社會學去了解人性，<br />\nMarketing 方面又要整到d 吸引嘅圖文對準目標對像。<br />\n好複雜，<br />\n相對上叫創新（因為無人算好成功），<br />\n而且呢d 搵唔到食嘅人，對好多人黎講都無吸引力。<br />\n但我覺得搞得過，人少少3,5,7 個開始囉，好似d 小教會咁。"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-30T01:54:38.000Z","msg":"點解香港人覺得冇錢賺既野就冇價值<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n心理質素好左先有動力去做更多既事<br />\n<br />\n我自己唔希望有一個人好似leader負責比意見<br />\n一做呢啲角色又係道德高地死得好快<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我希望係人人都係傾訴者同聆聽者<br />\n自己問題永遠都係自己負責<br />\n但大家可以互相支持<br />\n而唔係搵專業人士拎免費午餐<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-30T03:13:01.000Z","msg":"香港太細，文化太差。<br />\n社會有一種風氣，明明貧富懸殊極嚴重，<br />\n但搵唔到錢嘅就會好似被社會嘲笑咁。<br />\n當然都有一班人係願意做呢d 無錢嘅野，<br />\n不過難搵少少。<br />\n<br />\n我明你嘅追求。<br />\n不過因為普遍香港人嘅「傾訴」同埋「聆聽」能力都好差，即使係助人行業嘅社工，服務行業嘅客服，好多時都係亂9 黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />無同理心。我淨係見過資深心理學家愛輔導員識呢樣野咋。<br />\n<br />\n特別係，如果心理、社交非常健康嘅人，<br />\n佢家人同朋友等等身邊人都support 到佢啦，<br />\n參加得你都預左d 溝通障礙或者可能硬頸d。<br />\n香港好多人都有問題而不自覺架<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nPractically,<br />\n搞呢種Group 需要facilitator 而唔係leader，<br />\n有一兩個support 經驗豐富嘅人，<br />\n確保小組可以凝聚、不偏離本來嘅宗旨。<br />\n即係好似中學小組討論咁，<br />\n無d 人幫手將離題嘅人帶黎正題，<br />\n成個討論就會歪曲哂，大家一齊唔合格咁。<br />\n「自己問題自己負責」呢個concept，<br />\n好多香港人都要重新學習<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n當然，一開始整嘅門檻高d，<br />\n搞哂interview、background check、試用期，<br />\n都有機會遇到你理想中已經有咁嘅能力，<br />\n而又需要support group 嘅人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n慢慢發展唔難。<br />\n有心就得"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-30T03:46:30.000Z","msg":"多謝你完全明白我意思<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nFeel到搞黎都係消磨意志咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n「參加得你都預左d 溝通障礙或者可能硬頸d。」<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n救命<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"53dba4d463761836e78d4f1c2fe8a1c81ea8a9b5","tid":2180041,"uid":217128,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f9e2938ad754be11792baf586c26904aaa3f814e","tid":2180041,"uid":274732,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7435d03dc916e14e3a81b05c2190ecf1883bbe2b","tid":2180041,"uid":217128,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"a5ff4cdf095450f1aafba2d5e910ecd1cae5b427","tid":2180041,"uid":274732,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-30T01:54:38.000Z","msg":"點解香港人覺得冇錢賺既野就冇價值<img src=\"/assets